<p>NBC Learn, in partnership with the National Science Foundation, explores the impact that climate change is having on our planet. Their most recent video examines the impact of climate change on crops. Along with Prof. Bill Easterling at Penn State, Kelly discusses how shifts in temperature and CO2 will potentially impact crop production and food security</p>
